{"tid":1043220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[巴迷心聲］ 不得不承認，賤種蝗今晚其實贏左9成","createTime":"2019-03-02T05:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T07:01:44.000Z","uid":90515,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2fa250a6eba770da2e5373431feaa726f0069b2","tid":1043220,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"老老實實，雖然上場巴塞贏3粒，但唔好俾個比數呃左你，有睇場波都知根本成場都係蝗螞壓住巴塞黎打，迫到巴中場完全失控，全場起得4次腳，加上陣容年紀偏大，一半以上過曬30歲，上場只係谷埋最後嘅虛火出黎<br />\n<br />\n相反，賤種上場只係輸運，起腳多巴塞10次，雲尼素斯同個左閘撚到施美度同碧基仆曬街，黃金中場線又勁，如果好似以前餵阿朗咁餵賓周馬，一場起多十幾次門前起腳其實一啲都唔難，加上我相信VAR會及時回勇，根本皇馬未開波已經佔左9成優勢<br />\n<br />\n理性預測賤種蝗今晚贏3粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望咁多位賤迷贏完之後高抬貴手，抽少啲水<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，趕住買飛入潛艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214f32b86d88e5a82b24209b1ec5138f03491431","tid":1043220,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"希望唔好抽到乾塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbdb0c65bb464d9e28b63d0d564d5b9b1873e07","tid":1043220,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073864e4f2ca337bb21d78912c0632fa3724063d","tid":1043220,"uid":13543,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"師兄洗唔洗咁快燈定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e53b1d92677b77cb574002043ab2937bfa4cc1","tid":1043220,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"073864e4f2ca337bb21d78912c0632fa3724063d","tid":1043220,"uid":13543,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"師兄洗唔洗咁快燈定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"我都想燈，但理智話我聽今晚大勢已定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\